E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Look, I came back here after the service and I'd changed, man, I'd changed.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~服役结束我回来了，而且我变了，哥们。我变了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Oh, we got some very intense shit to handle.
~z~Yo. Shit. You serious as you wanna be. Pull that serious face and go kill people all you like.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~哟，操，你爱咋危险咋危险。板着危险的脸爱杀谁杀谁。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~The issue with what you were saying is that it's the money in the bank thing that people is having problems with right now.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你出的主意有问题，要用银行存款对吧，现在大家都没钱。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~If they look after themselves, that is. I am an equal opportunity lay. I'll fuck anything.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~只要她们保养得够好。我的床上人人平等，有什么睡什么。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~After some paperwork, I'll have what I need.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~加上点文书工作，我就能拿下目标了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I know, I fucking saw it, man.
~z~Brucie was a stock I'd short him all I could.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~如果Brucie是支股票，我一定会全力做空。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Yeah anyway, bro, that's besides the point. What we doing right now?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~不管怎么说，兄弟，咱跑题了。现在咱要干啥？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Maybe! If you're a schmuck like my brother, maybe. You see old B's over-exposed like a motherfucker.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~是吗？如果你和我弟弟一样傻逼那确实。你看看Brucie这孙子都装成什么样了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I just ain't the type of conventional businessman you might be used to, Lopez.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~只不过我不是随处可见的普通生意人罢了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Hey bro, I can't imagine you got much of a business left now we taken out all your employees.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~喂，老兄，干掉了这么多员工，你这生意不是白抢了？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Yeah. Okay. Fine. Whatever. Remind me what we are doing now?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~好，好吧。行，随你吧。我们是要干啥来着？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~We are paying a visit to some of my old uhh, business associates.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我们要拜访我的几位...生意伙伴。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I was doing time, bro. And leave my momma out of it.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我在坐牢，兄弟。别把我妈扯上。
~z~好极了。真他妈好。又他妈要开战。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Whoa, whoa, slow up, dog. I think you're mistaken in your impression of me. I look like a civilian to you?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~喔，喔，等等。你对我的印象好像有点问题。你看我像是平头百姓吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~You look like a lot of things, bro. A lot of neuroses in one tiny package. Kind of like an army knife without the edge.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你看着啥都像，兄弟。像小罐包装的神经病，像把没开刃的军刀。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Evidently, they are normally about twice your size and smart enough to stay in their office.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~那确实，普通生意人都比你高，也不会到写字楼外发疯。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Correct me if I'm wrong, but you and Tony are business partners, aren't you?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~一个猜想不一定对，你和Tony是生意伙伴，对吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Guys like you make guys like me rich.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~有你这种人在，我才能发大财。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Oh, how little you know, Luis. The assets aren't tangible.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~哦，你懂的太少了，Luis。资产未必是有形的。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~He's your brother, bro. Can't you help?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~他是你弟弟啊，老兄。不能帮一把？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Things I saw over there were insane, dog. Insane. I'd tell you about it but then I'd have to kill you right here.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~那时的光景实在疯狂，小子。太疯狂了。很想都告诉你，但说完就只能把你灭口了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I ain't going nowhere, bro. These bitches fired rockets at me. They're done.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我哪也不去，老兄。这些贱逼对我射火箭弹，他们死定了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Oh, God yeah! I can almost feel it.
~z~You see, the big businesses of the next decade are gonna get formed in this downturn,
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你看，下个十年的风口行业将在这次衰退中成型，

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~No, those guys are the assholes, Lou. Let's concentrate on what we're doing and get 'em.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~不，那些人才是混蛋，Lou。现在先干掉眼前的敌人。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I'm hoping you mean you got some boxes to move, something like that?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~希望你是说搬箱子之类的，是这样吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I mean, they can do whatever the fuck they like to you, you're annoying, but nobody fires rockets at me.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~他们怎么样你我都无所谓，你活该。但没人能拿火箭筒指我。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Well at this very moment there are fantastic opportunities for anyone with some money in a bank
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~在这非常时期，好机会都是留给银行有存款、

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Fuck, man, I hope you know what you doing.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我操，哥们，希望你知道自己在干啥。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Look, I done three years Israeli military - I've seen shit you wouldn't even believe.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~听着，我在以色列当了三年兵。经历说出来能吓死你。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I won't because I like you, heh. Special Forces don't even begin to describe my shit.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~没必要，因为我中意你，嘿嘿。特种部队的名号都配不上我的经历。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~What, do I got to turn around and smoke some more cats to prove myself to you?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~怎么，我非得回去杀几个人来证明自己吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Damn right, I'm angry. I can't believe I'm doing this shit, man. Not for some asshole Tony borrowed money off!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~太他妈对了，我怒了。我居然在干这种破事，老兄。还他妈是在替借钱给Tony的混蛋干活！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I seen a business that ain't been run well, so we're about to take the controlling share.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我看到了一家经营不善的企业，所以我们要接手股份。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~He's got debt you wouldn't believe and assets that don't exist.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~他的债多到你无法想象，资产全是空头支票。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~You still don't think I'm a serious motherfucker, do you?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你还是没拿我当危险人物，对吧？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~We're gonna take over their operation. Clear those fucks out.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我们要夺走他们的产业，干掉这帮混蛋。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I'm more than happy to leave everything to you, Mori. In fact, I don't wanna be no part of any of this shit.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~能当甩手掌柜真是我的荣幸，Mori。实际上，我一点都不想趟这些浑水。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~That's about as intense as I'm willing to get for you.
~z~You should try to stick your head out that club occasionally and soak up the atmosphere.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~偶尔也试着走出夜店，感受下外面的氛围吧。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Paperwork, bro. Maybe you should stick to that shit. Leave the field work to others.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~文书工作，老兄。你还是好好搞这块吧。体力活留给专业的。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~This is the first investment. Mergers and acquisitions, baby.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~这是第一笔投资。合并和收购，宝贝。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~That's a typical short sighted, negative viewpoint. Can't see your tiny hose through your bushy pubes.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你这属于是典型的鼠目寸光。隔了层屌毛就看不见自己的小屌了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Oh! Hah hah hah heh heh heh, yeah yeah. Fucking funny.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~哦！哈哈哈吼吼吼，对。真他妈逗。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~If someone could get a prize for buying at the top of the market, it'd be that sucker.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~如果要评「山顶买入奖」的话，评给他就对了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~For a man of your height, that's gotta be easy to do.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你这身高的人，都很容易上头。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~We are at a turning point in history, Luis. Right now. Things are turning.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我们正站在历史的拐点上，Luis。就是现在。时代变了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~In this climate there is more to think about than parties and plastic surgery.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~现在经济不景气，别老惦记你那派对跟整形了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Good thing too, bro. 'Cause a guy of your stature might find it tough if it was on anything higher than street level.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~真不错，兄弟。你这身高这辈子估计也只能在地上爬了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Well, I own Tony. Ergo, I own your ass as well. Get used to it.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~因为Tony是我的，所以你也是我的。慢慢习惯吧。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I guess you right. Things just turned shit.
~z~Those fucks tried to blow us up with a rocket launcher, man!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~那帮狗逼想拿火箭筒炸飞咱们，老兄！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Hey, how many guys got the juice to get into some Foreign Legion shit when they're 18?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~喂，有几个人刚18岁就有机会加入外国军队？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Why, bro, what's the excitement? We heading to a surprise party? You getting a sex op? What?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~咋了，老兄，有啥好激动的？我们是要去惊喜派对吗？还是你要变性了？啥啊？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Yeah, sure, bro, I was just getting facetious on you.
~z~Oh, I'm all about master plans. I got more than I know what to do with.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~噢，我最不愁的就是总体计划。我的计划比办法还多。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I'll whap that shit on the dashboard, see what you think of it. Yo yo, you'll think it's suddenly got dark in here.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我掏出来架仪表盘上，给你个机会评价。哟哟，一睁眼车里直接就黑了，

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Leave the disputes until later. Focus a little, okay?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~暂时先搁置争议，干掉对手，好吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~ I could do it, too... with my bare hands... wouldn't even think twice about it... but I won't, Lou.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我赤手空拳就能干掉你，眼睛都不会眨一下。但是没必要，Lou。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Yeah alright, alright, alright - where was I? Oh yeah, yeah, see, I love guys like you.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~好好好好。说到哪了？哦对对，我喜欢你这种人。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I told you about that hose shit, midget. It's creeping me the fuck out.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我说了别拿鸡巴说事了，矮逼。听得我反胃了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~What the fuck were they doing with a rocket launcher? What kind of business you trying to take over Mori?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~怎么他妈连火箭筒都出来了？你抢的是啥生意，Mori？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Oh, exciting times, Lou! These are some excitin' times. Hah hah!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~哦，激动人心啊！Lou！我已经按捺不住了。哈哈！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I done three years helping to run Hercules. I seen shit you wouldn't believe.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我帮大力神管了三年店。经历说出来能吓死你。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~MBA plus IDF equals "do not fuck with this bitch".
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~MBA + IDF = 这人你惹不起。~n~(MBA：工商管理硕士 IDF：以色列国防军)

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Oh, you got a lot to learn, driver.
~z~If you're pussying out, be my guest. You gonna write me a check?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你想逃的话，那请便。打算给我开支票吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Hey, just don't hold me responsible for your inadequacy issues after that, huh? Oh!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~发现自己太小可别怪我太大啊，好吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Ah, really, Lou? Cause if you got your mom's number there you know I might want to give her a call!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~啊，是吗，Lou？能给我她的电话号码吗？我这就去联系她！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I'm talking serious block the sun shit. Oh, hah!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~真的是遮天蔽日的大小。噢！哈哈！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~See, I've been bald since I was 19. I set the trends, I don't follow them.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我19岁就剃干净了。是我引领潮流，可不是反过来。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~This is the part where you ask me to hand over my life savings so you can "invest" it for me, right?"
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~这就是那套我把毕生积蓄掏出来给你，让你帮我「投资」对吧？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Mori, man, you're a business guy. So you should stick to your business shit.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~Mori啊，你是生意人。你就该好好做生意。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Hey, Lopez, you can start calling the shots when you don't owe me some major g's.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~喂，Lopez，等你没欠我那么多钱了，再对我发号施令吧。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I got it all, brother. I can handle anything.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~两个我都有，兄弟。我能解决一切。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Don't take nothing out, bro. Keep it to yourself. Keep the monster away from me, and listen to what I'm saying.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~别掏出来了，兄弟。你自己留着吧。怪兽还是离我远点吧，你好好听我说。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~A profitable one. I crunched the numbers, they came out gold. Now let's do it.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~是能捞钱的生意。我都算好了，大赚特赚。来吧。
~z~不是兄弟的问题，他早晚要摔在这儿。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~My moms might fall for that shit, but she believes that dogs bark at ghosts so maybe she's an easy touch.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我妈可能会被你骗到，但她还信狗能看见幽灵，她大概是高危人群。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~You think because of my lumpy little brother that I don't swing on the darkside.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~见着了我那大块头弟弟，你就觉得我不在道上浪吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Good for you, bro. You want to send me a resume so we can skip all this personal history crap?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~那就好，兄弟。要么你发我份简历吧，省得在这儿自我介绍。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~You were probably still sucking on your momma's titty at that age.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你那么大的时候可能还在吃奶吧。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~That a successful takeover, bro? Seems like we just killed some dudes and walked away with nothing.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~这算是抢夺成功了吗，老兄？好像我们只是杀了几个人就空手而归了。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I'm feeling bearish about him. Sell! Sell! Sell! God, sell!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~他这只股我看跌。抛！抛！抛！天哪，抛了吧！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Yo whoa what you mean? 'Cause she's old and wise? Hey, hey, hey I fuck cougars too, Luis.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~喂喂，你啥意思？因为她身经百战见得多了？喂喂喂，熟女我也能接受的，Luis。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~I never said you weren't a swinger, man. Come to think of it, I mighta seen you on one of them websites.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~我也没说你不是道上浪人啊。转念一想，我可能还在浪人队官网见过你。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~That's right, get angry, Lopez. Use it.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~你说得对，愤怒起来吧，Lopez。利用好它。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~and Mori K is gonna be there on the ground floor.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~而Mori K会抢先布局这些赛道。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Don't get involved in stuff that's out of your league because of some small man syndrome that makes you overcompensate.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~别因为气不过自己身材短小，就去做一些不自量力的事情。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Shave those things off, by the way. They're unappetising.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~有空记得把屌毛剃干净，真的恶心。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~This shit comes from the heart, okay? I don't wanna see you getting in over your head.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~全都是真心话，好吗？我不想看见你被冲昏头脑。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Check my bank balance, dog. I know exactly what I'm doing.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~看看我的银行余额吧，小子。在干啥我自有分寸。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Wow, it's incredible - he looks like a man, but he talks like a pussy.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~哇哦，太离谱了。你看起来像个爷们，说话跟个婆娘似的。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Funny, bro. Real funny. One thing I can rely on at least is mom knowing you were a little asshole if she met you.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~太搞笑了，兄弟。真的搞笑。有一点我敢肯定，我妈见到你就知道你不是啥好东西。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~and some balls in their sack. Cash is falling out of the sky!
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~胆子比天大的人的。天上到处掉馅饼！

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~No, I want you to understand, Luis, that I got the brain and the brawn. The meat and potatoes.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~不，我是想让你明白，Luis，我可是智勇双全。文武全能。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Still got my 4.0 though, didn't I? Ho, give it up, right here.
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~但我还是拿了4.0的绩点。嚯，好了，就说到这儿吧。

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Whoa, whoa, there's nothing small about what I got going on, Lopez. Yo, you need me to take out the monster?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~喔，喔，我跟短小二字可沾不上边啊，Lopez。哟，你要看看我的怪兽吗？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~Imagination isn't your strong suit, Luis. Let's leave the logistics to me, heh?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~想象力不是你的强项，Luis。组织人事的事我来，懂？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~So what's your master plan then, Mori? Where the billions coming from?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~所以你的总计划呢，Mori？上哪发大财呢？

E2BR1BA.original: ~z~You think it's easy sitting down to Econ 101 when you been icing fools?
E2BR1BA.translated: ~z~手里这么多人命，老实坐着听经济学原理哪有那么容易。
